Design Attributions
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project's local-model hardware-fit logic (GPU/VRAM and Apple unified-memory
ceiling selection, MoE active-parameter sizing) was informed by the design of
llmfit (https://github.com/AlexsJones/llmfit), MIT License. No llmfit code is
included or linked; only the approach was reused.
